trans-unit.source: An alternative way of installing this library into your code is to copy a single file manually into your working directory with language extension appropriate for your environment.

trans-unit.source: For trading with private APIs you need to obtain API keys from/to exchange markets. It often means registering with exchanges and creating API keys with your account. Most exchanges require personal info or identification. Some kind of verification may be necessary as well. If you want to trade you need to register yourself, this library will not create accounts or API keys for you. Some exchange APIs expose interface methods for registering an account from within the code itself, but most of exchanges don’t. You have to sign up and create API keys with their websites.
trans-unit.target: 要使用私有API进行交易，您需要从/到交易所市场获取API密钥。这通常意味着向交易所注册并使用您的帐户创建API密钥。大多数交易所要求提供个人信息或身份证明。也可能需要某种验证。如果您要交易，则需要注册自己，该库不会为您创建帐户或API密钥。一些交易所API公开了用于从代码本身内部注册帐户的接口方法，但是大多数交易所没有。您必须注册并使用其网站创建API密钥。

trans-unit.source: The anyex library is used to connect and trade with cryptocurrency / altcoin exchanges and payment processing services worldwide. It provides quick access to market data for storage, analysis, visualization, indicator development, algorithmic trading, strategy backtesting, bot programming, webshop integration and related software engineering.
trans-unit.target: 该anyex库是用来连接和与世界各国cryptocurrency / altcoin交流和支付处理服务贸易。它提供对市场数据的快速访问，以进行存储，分析，可视化，指标开发，算法交易，策略回测，机器人程序编程，网上商店集成和相关软件工程。

trans-unit.source: The anyex library consists of a public part and a private part. Anyone can use the public part out-of-the-box immediately after installation. Public APIs open access to public information from all exchange markets without registering user accounts and without having API keys.
trans-unit.target: Anyex库由公共部分和私有部分组成。任何人都可以在安装后立即使用公共部分。公共API开放访问所有交易所市场的公共信息,无需注册用户账户,也无需拥有API密钥。

trans-unit.source: The anyex library currently supports the following 114 cryptocurrency exchange markets and trading APIs:
trans-unit.target: Anyex库目前支持以下114个加密货币交易市场和交易API。

trans-unit.source: The anyex library supports both camelcase notation (preferred in JavaScript) and underscore notation (preferred in Python and PHP), therefore all methods can be called in either notation or coding style in any language.
trans-unit.target: anyex库同时支持驼色符号(JavaScript中首选)和下划线符号(Python和PHP中首选),因此,所有的方法都可以在任何语言中以任何一种符号或编码风格调用。

trans-unit.source: The easiest way to install the anyex library is to use builtin package managers:
trans-unit.target: 安装anyex库最简单的方法是使用内置的包管理器。

trans-unit.source: The library is under MIT license, that means it’s absolutely free for any developer to build commercial and opensource software on top of it, but use it at your own risk with no warranties, as is.
trans-unit.target: 该库已获得MIT许可，这意味着任何开发人员都可以免费在其上构建商业和开源软件，但是使用该库的风险由您自己承担，没有任何担保。

trans-unit.source: The library supports concurrent asynchronous mode with asyncio and async/await in Python 3.5.3+
trans-unit.target: 该库在Python 3.5.3+中支持asyncio和async/await的并发异步模式。

trans-unit.source: The list above is updated frequently, new crypto markets, altcoin exchanges, bug fixes, API endpoints are introduced and added on a regular basis. See the Manual for details. If you don’t find a cryptocurrency exchange market in the list above and/or want another exchange to be added, post or send us a link to it by opening an issue here on GitHub or via email.
trans-unit.target: 上面的列表会经常更新，会定期引入和添加新的加密货币市场，山寨币交换，错误修复，API端点。有关详细信息，请参见手册。如果您在上面的列表中找不到加密货币交易市场和/或想要添加其他交易所，请在GitHub或通过电子邮件在此处打开问题来发布或发送给我们链接。
